{"title":"荐歌：遥不可及的你（花粥）","slug":"荐歌：遥不可及的你（花粥）","date":"2022-07-22T13:29:29.000Z","updated":"2022-07-22T13:30:46.051Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/荐歌：遥不可及的你（花粥）.json","excerpt":"文章来自微信公众号“科文路”，欢迎关注、互动。转发须注明出处。凉爽的周五快乐！本周的荐歌来自花粥，《遥不可及的你》。花粥的唱功很普通，但嗓音总透露着淡淡的忧伤，这首歌更甚。能把她自己的歌唱到人心，就像一个多年的好友​对你吐露心声。喜欢。也希望你们都是歌里那个“温暖的人”。下面是 live 版本，乐器更丰富些，","covers":null,"content":"<blockquote>\n<p>文章来自微信公众号“科文路”，欢迎关注、互动。转发须注明出处。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>凉爽的周五快乐！</p>\n<p>本周的荐歌来自花粥，《遥不可及的你》。</p>\n<iframe frameborder=\"no\" border=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" width=330 height=86 src=\"//music.163.com/outchain/player?type=2&id=450853439&auto=1&height=66\"></iframe>\n\n<p>花粥的唱功很普通，但嗓音总透露着淡淡的忧伤，这首歌更甚。能把她自己的歌唱到人心，就像一个多年的好友​对你吐露心声。</p>\n<p>喜欢。</p>\n<p>也希望你们都是歌里那个“温暖的人”。</p>\n<p>下面是 live 版本，乐器更丰富些，</p>\n<iframe frameborder=\"no\" border=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" width=330 height=86 src=\"//music.163.com/outchain/player?type=2&id=1433736573&auto=1&height=66\"></iframe>\n\n<span id=\"more\"></span>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br><span class=\"line\">25</span><br><span class=\"line\">26</span><br><span class=\"line\">27</span><br><span class=\"line\">28</span><br><span class=\"line\">29</span><br><span class=\"line\">30</span><br><span class=\"line\">31</span><br><span class=\"line\">32</span><br><span class=\"line\">33</span><br><span class=\"line\">34</span><br><span class=\"line\">35</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">作词 : 花粥</span><br><span class=\"line\">作曲 : 花粥</span><br><span class=\"line\">如果有一天我要去流浪</span><br><span class=\"line\">不是因为我厌倦了家乡</span><br><span class=\"line\">不是难忍这里的冬天太长</span><br><span class=\"line\">而是我终于得知了你的方向</span><br><span class=\"line\">如果有一天我不再感伤</span><br><span class=\"line\">不是因为我突然的成长</span><br><span class=\"line\">不是有天有人向我递一颗糖</span><br><span class=\"line\">而是我终于走到了你的身旁</span><br><span class=\"line\">我从前相信</span><br><span class=\"line\">这世上有一个温暖的人</span><br><span class=\"line\">只为我悲喜</span><br><span class=\"line\">为我阻挡着人间的锋利</span><br><span class=\"line\">为了找到你</span><br><span class=\"line\">从未放过任何蛛丝马迹</span><br><span class=\"line\">而事到如今</span><br><span class=\"line\">终于明白我命里没你</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">我曾遇到许多美丽故事</span><br><span class=\"line\">也曾以为那些是你的名字</span><br><span class=\"line\">我的执迷不悟感动了我自己</span><br><span class=\"line\">你却还是一样遥不可及</span><br><span class=\"line\">所以我开始向往着远方</span><br><span class=\"line\">想去那些曾经有你的地方</span><br><span class=\"line\">可我未曾想过的人海茫茫</span><br><span class=\"line\">让我没日没夜迷失方向</span><br><span class=\"line\">我从前相信</span><br><span class=\"line\">这世上有一个温暖的人</span><br><span class=\"line\">只为我悲喜</span><br><span class=\"line\">为我阻挡着人间的锋利</span><br><span class=\"line\">为了找到你</span><br><span class=\"line\">从未放过任何蛛丝马迹</span><br><span class=\"line\">而事到如今</span><br><span class=\"line\">终于明白我命里没你</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p><strong>都看到这儿了，不如关注每日推送的“科文路”、互动起来~</strong></p>\n<p><strong>至少点个赞再走吧~</strong></p>\n","more":"<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</sp